THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:22.323 --> 00:24.258
- 16 MURDERS
OVER FOURTH OF JULY.

00:24.258 --> 00:26.260
- THEY CUT BACK
ON THE STOP-AND-SEARCHES,

00:26.260 --> 00:27.628
