DECLARED HIM FIT FOR DUTY.

00:42.443 --> 00:45.313
- 1 PP.
WELCOME TO THE PUZZLE PALACE.

00:45.313 --> 00:46.747
- BUT THEY DID SAY
THAT HE WAS COMING BACK.

00:46.747 --> 00:48.349
- FAR AS I KNOW.

00:48.349 --> 00:50.384
