THINKING SOME THINGS OVER.

00:50.384 --> 00:53.387
I'D LIKE TO MOVE SOME PIECES
AROUND ON THE BOARD.

00:53.387 --> 00:55.389
- YOU CAN MOVE ME
BACK TO FRANCE.

00:55.389 --> 00:56.790
- ACTUALLY, I'M JUST
TEAMING YOU UP BACK UP

00:56.790 --> 00:58.459
WITH YOUR OLD PARTNER.
- REALLY?

00:58.459 --> 00:59.860
- CAPTAIN, FIN AND I HAVE
BEEN KIND OF--

00:59.860 --> 01:01.762
- GETTING TO THAT.
I'D LIKE TO...

01:01.762 --> 01:03.464
