WITH YOU, NICK?

01:17.811 --> 01:19.580
- IT'S ALL GOOD.

01:19.580 --> 01:21.782
- OKAY THEN.

01:27.188 --> 01:29.457
- NICK...
JUST SO YOU KNOW,

01:29.457 --> 01:32.326
