TO MAKE THAT SWITCH.

01:32.326 --> 01:36.330
- I KNOW YOU DIDN'T.
I DID.

01:36.330 --> 01:38.332
- YOU DID?

01:38.332 --> 01:41.869
- LIV...IT'S NO BIG DEAL.

01:41.869 --> 01:43.404
ONE THING ABOUT YOU...

01:43.404 --> 01:45.273
YOU NEED TO HAVE
A PARTNER YOU CAN TRUST.

01:52.246 --> 01:53.781
- THERE IS NO THERE THERE.
- I TRUST HIM MORE

01:53.781 --> 01:56.650
THAN SOME GUY WHO CLAIMS
HE WAS BORN IN HAWAII,

01:56.650 --> 01:59.253
GREW UP IN INDONESIA,
WENT TO A MADRASAH--

01:59.253 --> 02:01.189
- OOH, A MADRASAH.
WELL, THAT'S SCARY.

02:01.189 --> 02:02.390
THAT'S NOT LIKE
AN OFFSHORE TAX HAVEN, IS IT?

02:02.390 --> 02:04.492
[knock at door]
- PUNCHING OUT, BOSS.

02:04.492 --> 02:06.594
YOU AN ADAM CAIN FAN?

02:06.594 --> 02:09.797
- NO, IT'S JUST WHITE NOISE
FOR THE PAPERWORK.

02:09.797 --> 02:11.232
- MM-HMM.

02:11.232 --> 02:12.700
- SO HOW'D MY NEW LINEUP
GO OVER TODAY?

02:12.700 --> 02:14.235
- LIKE A LEAD BALLOON.

02:14.235 --> 02:15.803
