OF THE NIGHT OFF.

02:21.275 --> 02:24.278
- [laughs]
OKAY.

02:24.278 --> 02:25.413
- THAT'S RIGHT.
THAT'S RAISING CAIN.

02:25.413 --> 02:27.248
THAT'S RIGHT.
AND YOU KNOW WHAT?

02:27.248 --> 02:28.416
I'D LIKE TO RAISE
A LITTLE CAIN WITH YOU.

02:28.416 --> 02:30.284
LISA,
THANKS FOR YOUR USUAL

02:30.284 --> 02:32.720
COMPASSIONATE,
ANTEBELLUM ANALYSIS.

02:32.720 --> 02:35.323
FOLKS, FOUR MORE MONTHS
OF THIS TORTURE

02:35.323 --> 02:36.757
UNTIL THE ELECTION.

02:36.757 --> 02:38.392
