WOMEN'S ATTITUDES TOWARD SEX.

02:51.239 --> 02:53.641
I'M JUST GLAD
THEY WANT IT ALL.

02:53.641 --> 02:56.677
NOW HER BOOK MAKES FIFTY SHADES
LOOK LIKE A DISNEY STORY.

02:56.677 --> 03:00.414
SHE IS HOT, RICH, KINKY.

03:00.414 --> 03:02.216
I THINK I'M IN LOVE.

03:02.216 --> 03:04.352
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
JOCELYN PALEY.

03:04.352 --> 03:09.223
[applause]

03:09.223 --> 03:11.392
I DON'T KNOW IF I SHOULD
KISS YOU OR SPANK YOU.

03:11.392 --> 03:13.294
- WHO SAYS
YOU CAN'T DO BOTH?

03:13.294 --> 03:15.329
[laughter]
- PLEASE.

03:15.329 --> 03:17.365
YOU DID GREAT.
THE AUDIENCE LOVED YOU.

03:17.365 --> 03:19.733
- ONLY BECAUSE
I HAD A GOOD PARTNER.

03:22.236 --> 03:24.405
SO...

03:24.405 --> 03:27.408
ADAM...

03:27.408 --> 03:29.843
WHAT'S YOUR FANTASY?

03:40.321 --> 03:42.990
[both chuckling]

03:48.262 --> 03:50.331
[buttons clattering on floor]

03:52.032 --> 03:55.369
- ACT TWO.
I SAY WHEN YOU CAN TOUCH ME.

03:55.369 --> 03:57.338
- WELL, I'M SORRY, SIR.
- TURN AROUND.

03:57.338 --> 04:00.574
GET ON THE BED.

04:00.574 --> 04:03.311
NO, NO, ON ALL FOURS.

04:07.581 --> 04:10.384
YOU NEED TO BE PUNISHED.

04:10.384 --> 04:11.452
[thwack]
- AH!

04:11.452 --> 04:13.787
