04:17.525 --> 04:20.861
- YOU DON'T TELL ME...
WHAT TO DO.

04:20.861 --> 04:23.397
- [gasping]

05:13.681 --> 05:15.383
- SARA PALERMO,
JOCELYN'S BOOK TOUR ESCORT.

05:15.383 --> 05:16.850
- RIGHT.
YOU CALLED 911.

05:16.850 --> 05:19.453
- I WENT TO HER HOTEL
TO TAKE HER TO A RADIO SHOW.

05:19.453 --> 05:21.555
