ON HER NIGHTGOWN.

05:21.555 --> 05:23.023
- OKAY, DID SHE
TELL YOU WHAT HAPPENED?

05:23.023 --> 05:24.858
- SHE KEEPS SAYING
NOTHING HAPPENED,

05:24.858 --> 05:26.760
BUT SHE HAS BRUISES
AND A MARK ON HER NECK.

05:26.760 --> 05:28.696
- OKAY, AND WHEN'S
THE LAST TIME YOU SAW HER

05:28.696 --> 05:30.698
BEFORE ALL OF THAT?
- SHE HAD A TAPING YESTERDAY.

05:30.698 --> 05:32.666
ADAM CAIN.
- THE TALK SHOW HOST.

05:32.666 --> 05:34.702
- HE ASKED HER OUT AFTER.
SHE WAS SKY HIGH.

05:34.702 --> 05:37.771
TODAY NOT A WORD.
WHAT'S THAT SOUND LIKE TO YOU?

05:37.771 --> 05:39.139
- I WASN'T RAPED.

05:39.139 --> 05:41.675
I DIDN'T ASK HER
TO CALL THE POLICE.

05:41.675 --> 05:43.477
- OKAY, BUT THERE'S...
PAPERWORK.

05:43.477 --> 05:46.547
CAN YOU JUST CONFIRM THAT YOU
WERE ON A DATE WITH MR. CAIN?

05:46.547 --> 05:48.682
- JUST FOR DRINKS,
THEN HIS PLACE.

05:48.682 --> 05:50.418
- THAT BRUISE ON YOUR NECK.

05:50.418 --> 05:51.719
THAT FROM HIM?

05:51.719 --> 05:53.421
- HE GOT A LITTLE HANDSY.

05:53.421 --> 05:56.390
- BECAUSE IT REALLY LOOKS
MORE LIKE A BELT DID IT.

05:56.390 --> 05:58.426
- DID YOU ASK HIM
TO DO THAT TO YOU?

05:58.426 --> 06:01.629
- NO, BUT I THINK HE THOUGHT
IT WAS PART OF THE SEX.

06:01.629 --> 06:04.632
- SO YOU DID HAVE SEX.

06:04.632 --> 06:06.567
- [stammering]
HE--HE...

06:06.567 --> 06:09.737
PUT IT INSIDE ME,
BUT NOT WHERE I WAS USED TO.

06:11.405 --> 06:13.607
- DID YOU TELL HIM TO STOP?

06:13.607 --> 06:14.575
- I TRIED.

06:14.575 --> 06:16.977
HE PULLED THE BELT SO TIGHT,
I COULDN'T TALK.

06:16.977 --> 06:21.048
