TO DOMINATE ME.

06:23.551 --> 06:25.986
I DON'T SEE HOW I CAN
CALL THAT RAPE.

06:25.986 --> 06:28.055
- OKAY, WELL, WE DON'T HAVE
TO DECIDE THAT RIGHT NOW.

06:28.055 --> 06:30.824
BUT IN THE MEANTIME...
YOU SHOULD DO A RAPE KIT.

06:30.824 --> 06:32.560
JUST IN CASE.

06:32.560 --> 06:33.594
- I WON'T NEED IT.

06:33.594 --> 06:36.697
- DID HE USE A CONDOM?

06:36.697 --> 06:39.800
HONEY, YOU'RE GONNA NEED
TO GET TESTED FOR STDs.

06:43.571 --> 06:45.205
- SCARING SOMEONE
INTO GETTING A RAPE KIT?

06:45.205 --> 06:47.708
SOMETIMES IT'S BETTER
TO BUILD TRUST.

06:47.708 --> 06:48.976
- IT'S NOT GONNA MATTER
EITHER WAY.

06:48.976 --> 06:50.744
HAVE YOU READ HER BOOK?
- NO.

06:50.744 --> 06:52.646
- MY SISTER GAVE IT TO ME,
RIGHT?

06:52.646 --> 06:54.648
IN ACT FIVE,
THE MAIN CHARACTER

06:54.648 --> 06:56.617
IS CHOKED WITH A BELT
AND SODOMIZED.

06:56.617 --> 06:58.686
SHE HAS, LIKE, 18 ORGASMS.

06:58.686 --> 07:00.888
- GREAT.
THAT'S A BEST-SELLER.

07:00.888 --> 07:02.556
- AND FOR YOU PERSONALLY,

07:02.556 --> 07:03.991
HOW ARE YOU DEALING
WITH ALL THIS ATTENTION?

07:03.991 --> 07:06.594
- MY LIFE FEELS
A LITTLE OUT OF CONTROL.

07:06.594 --> 07:07.761
- SOME DISCIPLINE MIGHT HELP.
OR HURT.

07:07.761 --> 07:09.763
- IDEALLY, BOTH.

07:09.763 --> 07:11.465
- WELL, STAY WITH US,
AMERICA.

07:11.465 --> 07:12.833
WE'LL BE RIGHT BACK
AFTER THIS BREAK.

07:12.833 --> 07:14.602
[applause]
OR MAYBE WE WON'T.

07:14.602 --> 07:16.069
- SHE'S GIVING
AS GOOD AS SHE GETS HERE.

07:16.069 --> 07:18.606
- BUT IT TURNED UGLY
WHEN THEY WERE ALONE.

07:18.606 --> 07:21.208
