BUT SHE AGREED TO A RAPE KIT?

07:21.208 --> 07:23.711
- WELL, RELUCTANTLY.
SHE HAS ANAL FISSURES

07:23.711 --> 07:25.746
AND A SEVERE LIGATURE MARK
ON HER NECK.

07:25.746 --> 07:27.080
- SHE DIDN'T PRESS CHARGES?

07:27.080 --> 07:28.582
- NO, SHE'S WORRIED,
YOU KNOW,

07:28.582 --> 07:30.884
BECAUSE OF HER BOOK.

07:30.884 --> 07:32.920
- HER PROSE IS PRETTY FLORID,
ALTHOUGH I ADMIRE ANY AUTHOR

07:32.920 --> 07:36.256
WHO CAN WORK IN NIPPLE CLAMPS
AND ALBINONI'S ADAGIO

07:36.256 --> 07:38.158
IN ONE SENTENCE.
- YOU READ THIS?

07:38.158 --> 07:40.093
- THE YENTAS AT MY MOTHER'S
RETIREMENT HOME

07:40.093 --> 07:42.663
WERE PASSING IT AROUND AND
MY MOTHER'S LOSING HER SIGHT,

07:42.663 --> 07:44.932
SO I READ IT TO HER.
- OKAY, THIS ISN'T A BOOK CLUB.

07:44.932 --> 07:47.701
