WHY ARE WE WASTING OUR TIME?

07:50.538 --> 07:53.674
- CAPTAIN,
YOU'RE NEW TO SVU.

07:53.674 --> 07:57.578
VICTIMS SOMETIMES TAKE TIME
TO PROCESS.

07:57.578 --> 07:59.747
SHE SAID STOP.
HE TIGHTENED THE BELT.

07:59.747 --> 08:01.849
HE PROBABLY THOUGHT THAT,
GIVEN HER BOOK,

08:01.849 --> 08:03.150
