OF THE GOOD GUYS.

08:15.563 --> 08:16.997
- WE'VE SEEN HIM AT BENEFITS.

08:16.997 --> 08:18.599
POLICE WIDOWS, BATTERED WOMEN.

08:18.599 --> 08:19.700
HE NEVER SAYS NO.

08:19.700 --> 08:22.235
- YOU MEAN HE NEVER HEARS NO.
- OKAY.

08:22.235 --> 08:24.738
FIN AND MUNCH,
PAY CAIN A FRIENDLY VISIT

08:24.738 --> 08:27.140
