BEFORE HE LAWYERS UP.

08:27.140 --> 08:29.810
BENSON, ROLLINS,
CHECK AND SEE

08:29.810 --> 08:31.879
IF JOCELYN'S
HAD TIME TO PROCESS.

08:31.879 --> 08:36.684
