PLEASE.

09:04.344 --> 09:06.113
- ADAM CAIN.
- YEAH, HEY!

09:06.113 --> 09:07.781
DETECTIVE MUNCH, RIGHT?
YEAH.

09:07.781 --> 09:09.717
PLEASE DON'T SHOOT ME.
I'M A BLEEDER.

09:09.717 --> 09:11.752
- YOU REMEMBER MY PARTNER FIN?
