ON YOUR SHOW LAST NIGHT.

09:20.360 --> 09:21.729
- YEAH, THAT'S RIGHT.
WHY?

09:21.729 --> 09:23.797
- YOU TWO WENT OUT
TO DINNER AFTER?

09:23.797 --> 09:25.232
- COME ON, GUYS.
DON'T SANDBAG ME.

09:25.232 --> 09:27.100
IS JOSS OKAY?
