09:27.100 --> 09:28.335
- SHE MAY HAVE BEEN ASSAULTED.

09:28.335 --> 09:30.237
- OH, MY GOD.

09:30.237 --> 09:33.741
I PUT HER IN A CAR SERVICE
LAST NIGHT AT 1:00.

09:33.741 --> 09:36.309
SHE SEEMED FINE.
JUST A LITTLE TIPSY, BUT...

09:36.309 --> 09:37.911
WAS IT THE DRIVER?

09:37.911 --> 09:39.747
- NOTHING ROUGH
BETWEEN YOU TWO?

09:39.747 --> 09:42.249
- SERIOUSLY?
