09:42.249 --> 09:44.151
- WHY DON'T YOU TELL US
YOUR SIDE?

09:44.151 --> 09:46.787
- [laughs]
OH, JEEZ.

09:49.723 --> 09:51.158
YOU KNOW HER BOOK, RIGHT?

09:51.158 --> 09:53.060
