A FEW SCENES.

09:53.060 --> 09:56.163
SHE WANTED ME TO THROW HER DOWN
AND...TAKE CONTROL.

09:56.163 --> 09:58.398
- WHOSE IDEA WAS THE BELT?

09:58.398 --> 10:01.735
- THAT?
THAT WAS HERS.

10:01.735 --> 10:03.203
- YOU SAID YOU
WERE IN CONTROL.

10:03.203 --> 10:06.273
- EVERYTHING THAT HAPPENED
BETWEEN US WAS CONSENSUAL.

10:06.273 --> 10:07.908
