10:11.712 --> 10:13.180
NOW I KNOW YOU GUYS
GOT BETTER THINGS TO DO.

10:13.180 --> 10:14.848
I KNOW I DO.
I GOT A SHOW TO PREP.

10:14.848 --> 10:17.184
I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

10:17.184 --> 10:19.687
- THE GUY SEEM TESTY TO YOU?

10:19.687 --> 10:23.356
- NO CHARGES FILED,
AND I HATE THIS CASE ALREADY.

10:26.393 --> 10:28.762
- I HADN'T HAD AN ORGASM
SINCE I HAD MY THIRD KID,

10:28.762 --> 10:30.998
AND THEN I READ YOUR BOOK.
- FOUND YOUR INNER VENUS?

10:30.998 --> 10:33.400
- AND THEN SOME. HEY,
CAN YOU MAKE THAT OUT TO JACK?

10:33.400 --> 10:37.004
MY HUSBAND IS YOUR BIGGEST FAN.
- JOCELYN.

10:37.004 --> 10:38.672
- UH, I'M A LITTLE BUSY.

10:38.672 --> 10:41.041
- WE WON'T TAKE UP MUCH TIME.

10:45.713 --> 10:47.180
