10:49.349 --> 10:51.451
- JOCELYN, YOU HAD
SOME PRETTY SERIOUS INJURIES.

10:51.451 --> 10:54.387
YOU MAY WANNA
TAKE IT EASY.

10:54.387 --> 10:55.723
- THEY GAVE ME TYLENOL
AND CODEINE.

10:55.723 --> 10:57.257
