11:20.347 --> 11:23.817
- IF YOU NEED US...
WILL YOU CALL?

11:28.756 --> 11:31.391
- ALL RIGHT!
WHO'S NEXT?

11:31.391 --> 11:32.860
[woman murmurs]

11:32.860 --> 11:36.396
[background chatter]

11:36.396 --> 11:39.767
- YOU'VE CERTAINLY TURNED
THE PUBLISHING WORLD ON END.

11:39.767 --> 11:42.302
WHICH I GATHER IS A POSITION
YOU LIKE AS WELL.

11:44.104 --> 11:45.739
- A TOAST!
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,

11:45.739 --> 11:47.440
